The paper deals with image segmentation, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed framework involves a learning approach for selecting the best resolution, which suggests the involvement of machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also mentions medical imaging, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM).
